.TP
\fB\-w\fR, \fB\-\-wait\fR
wait for a key\-stroke before starting.
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
print version information and exit
.TP
\fB\-z\fR, \fB\-\-timezone\fR tz
